sector_narrative: Removal of land mines and explosive remnants of war
description_narrative: Funding under this initiative support administrative management of the Global Mine Action Program including public relations and advocacy. The Global Mine Action Program comprises support to key international organisations undertaking global mine action work. The total value of this initiative is $32.5 thousand expenced in the 2010-11 financial year.
